  "time_ut": 1657552276,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u2018\u2018\u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0db1 \u0d85\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dba \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd2.\u0d91\u0db8\u0dca.\u0d91\u0dc6\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0da0\u0dca\u0da1\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca\u2018\u2018",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"Political instability hinders IMF talks\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dr. Nandalal Weerasinghe has stated in the interview with Reuters that the long-term political instability in Sri Lanka may delay the progress of the IMF loan assistance negotiations.",
        "He said that Dr. Nandalal Weerasinghe will resign from the post if there is no political stability in Sri Lanka, since last April, he will participate in the negotiations to get the support of the International Monetary Fund.",
        "Mr. Nandalal Weerasinghe, Governor of the Central Bank of Sri Lanka, stated that political stability should be established in Sri Lanka very soon, mainly to make progress in our discussions with the International Monetary Fund and to find solutions to the shortage of fuel, gas and essential commodities.",
        "Reuters reported that Dr. Nandalal Weerasinghe said in an interview with Reuters that he will serve as Central Bank Governor until the completion of his appointed six-year term.",
        "Also, Dr. Nandalal Weerasinghe mentioned that negotiations are being held with India to obtain a foreign currency exchange facility of US$ 1 billion from the Central Bank of India.",
        "Dr. Nandalal Weerasinghe further stated that the United States of America is negotiating with India to obtain a loan facility of 500 million dollars for the purchase of fuel."
      ],
